{"tid":1365933,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"英雄聯盟之對抗中國","createTime":"2019-07-25T20:12:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T19:17:02.000Z","uid":46072,"like":165,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9e7a1956076dbba60fbb99537ac37e2e539f1b02","tid":1365933,"uid":46072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:12:43.000Z","msg":"有啲長，希望大家睇哂佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n小弟平時都會睇英雄聯盟比賽，近排sem break搵左份part time黎做，去左國際英雄聯盟高校賽幫手。<br />\n今日第一日打比賽，我俾人sd左去總控制室，可以話係成個比賽既指揮中心。入面幾個全部都係大陸人，中國騰訊派黎，而且比賽ser係國服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己一個香港人坐係入面好奇怪，但明明呢到係香港。<br />\n到比賽開始，細舞台第一場係香港中大對中國集美大學隊。中大五個選手個名後面都加左呢兩個月黎遊行抗爭既日子，一開始班大陸人唔明，以為係生日日期，但又開始懷疑點解全部都係夏天生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。佢地就搵點解，但係用百度唔係用google。我一直都無出聲，但最後佢地都知道係同近期社會運動有關。<br />\n佢地知道左之後好大反應，特別係因為呢個比賽中國斗魚有直播，但好可惜比賽係喺副舞台無進行直播，所以大概只有間房既人知道呢件事。如果呢件事係主舞台發生後果不堪設想。<br />\n後來佢地仲刪埋呢場比賽既record，好驚會流出，同埋即刻叫cuhk選手改名。<br />\n咁始終都係正式競技，唔好牽涉太多政治野我都理解。但之後發生既野我就好唔明白<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KuVnfEv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKuVnfEv.jpg&h=0fc35fe9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後cu出場既時候拍左段vod，原來一開始就比過班中國人去censor，佢地要求舞台刪左呢句野但無刪到兼播到去中國，完全唔明句野有咩問題要ban，到佢地到主舞台正式比賽時<span style=\"color: red;\">仲驚佢地係選手鏡頭前面展示標語俾中國見到</span>，話一見到有咩唔對路就閂左啲鏡頭，要搜佢地身先俾上主舞台。但見到啲中國人又憤怒又淆底個樣真係好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iudoH57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiudoH57.jpg&h=5e55a602&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每次見到香港隊出場都會好興奮係後台支持，今日日比賽完三勝一敗好有幾會出線，希望大家都多多支持佢地，如果識佢地既就share出去俾佢地見到!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66fdaa7957eb29eb55d6353cff02607f36cfb377","tid":1365933,"uid":46072,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:15:53.000Z","msg":"今日會繼續有比賽打，所以捱眼訓都想打左今日所見所聞出黎先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2443638ea3e7c98e48db2e6822007aa184a32fe","tid":1365933,"uid":69610,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T20:19:35.000Z","msg":"電競抗爭"},{"pid":"bb68b37014bc488c65c17821dac7a14a6fa70a23","tid":1365933,"uid":84697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:33:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0036f00bb3f7b8dfe6ad7f7a1a72289a2ad15b","tid":1365933,"uid":105511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:42:23.000Z","msg":"Respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59da40b2fcf3d800c76a29856c993ae1edeaabe6","tid":1365933,"uid":138920,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:47:44.000Z","msg":"暴大學生從來都唔會令我失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79d79c3f21740cf38ee62834068b3b33f5cba654","tid":1365933,"uid":120084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:55:12.000Z","msg":"Respect"},{"pid":"d642b0899f02d032295ddf032d3c173024575769","tid":1365933,"uid":50847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"respect"},{"pid":"0eb472052675b723456dc3f1ac6336ea16aa82da","tid":1365933,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T01:58:06.000Z","msg":"無論去到邊都總有支那撚係到<br />\n世界毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64c6f618d4225469c1351449a7d6ea0494a06214","tid":1365933,"uid":52194,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"所謂電莖師<br />\n香港又幾多公司會支持？<br />\n咪又